Step to reproduce:
When using a hybrid property as follows:
```python
@hybrid_property
    def email(self):
        return self._email

    @email.setter
    def email(self, email):
        self._email = email
```
 In raw SQL query, you get order by table.email (the email column doesn't exist in the actual table) instead of order by table._email
A possible fix for this is here: https://github.com/shubham-padia/flask-rest-jsonapi/commit/3c622710168c97ed56d6a827ec7e75c2fe0ee9ca
If this seems okay, I can make a PR for it :) .

